<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="676">Davis &amp; Hedge Festschr</emphasis>
.: 139. 1989) later restricting this to the leaves, which he identified as of 
<taxonomicName authority="Herter. To" authorityName="Herter. To" authorityYear="1948" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Mimosa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vellosiella">
